      <div class="span7 offset1">
        <p>Health Republic Insurance of New York is a true not-for-profit program and New York’s only CO-OP -- Consumer Operated and Oriented Plan.&nbsp; CO-OPs are private, member-governed health insurance companies forming across the country as part of the Affordable Care Act. &nbsp;Health Republic Insurance of New York is one of 23 CO-OPs nationally.</p>

      </div>

